iulib - the image understanding library
http://code.google.com/p/iulib/

Version 0.3 (2008-10-15)

Please refer to the site (http://code.google.com/p/iulib/) for insructions.
Please refer to INSTALL document for installation instructions.

-----
colib
-----

The core component of iulib that is so generic that it even does not know about
images is called `colib'. It is a header-only library that installs into colib/
subfolder of the include path. A single header, "colib.h", includes all others.
